This paper deals with the design and analysis of an algorithm for LTE femtocell-macrocell networks, which involves network optimization and modeling of user mobility behaviors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and optimization, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) as the second likely category. The paper also deals with system-level analysis and modeling, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the third likely category. The paper also involves multimedia communication and traffic offloading, which suggests cs.MM (Multimedia) as the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper also involves security and privacy issues related to signaling overhead, which suggests cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the fifth likely category.
